---
import LogoMark from "./LogoMark.astro";
---
<section class="ai-section" id="ia">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="eyebrow-row reveal">
      <span class="tick"></span> Inteligencia artificial &middot; Nuevo
    </div>
    <h2 class="section__h2 reveal reveal--lag-1">
      Mandale una foto.<br />INOUT registra solo.
    </h2>
    <p class="section__lead reveal reveal--lag-2">
      Saca foto al recibo y mandala por WhatsApp, o pidele al chatbot dentro de la app. La IA detecta comercio, monto, categoria y fecha. Tu confirmas con un toque &mdash; sin abrir la app si no quieres.
    </p>

    <div class="ai-grid reveal reveal--lag-3">
      <article class="chat-card" aria-label="Ejemplo de chat con el asistente INOUT">
        <header class="chat-card__header">
          <div class="chat-card__avatar">
            <LogoMark />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="chat-card__title">INOUT &middot; Asistente</div>
            <div class="chat-card__sub">
              <span class="live"></span> via WhatsApp &middot; en linea
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chat-card__verified">
            <i data-lucide="badge-check"></i> Verificado
          </div>
        </header>

        <div class="chat-card__body">
          <div class="bubble bubble--user">
            <div class="bubble__photo">
              <div class="receipt">
                <div class="receipt__title">TOTTUS</div>
                <div class="receipt__sub">SUPERMERCADO &middot; TICKET</div>
                <div class="receipt__sep"></div>
                <div class="receipt__row"><span>PAN INTEGRAL</span><span>S/ 8.90</span></div>
                <div class="receipt__row"><span>LECHE 1L x2</span><span>S/ 12.40</span></div>
                <div class="receipt__row"><span>PALTA HASS</span><span>S/ 14.10</span></div>
                <div class="receipt__row"><span>ARROZ COSTE&Ntilde;O</span><span>S/ 22.00</span></div>
                <div class="receipt__row"><span>POLLO 1.2KG</span><span>S/ 30.00</span></div>
                <div class="receipt__sep"></div>
                <div class="receipt__total"><span>TOTAL</span><span>S/ 87.40</span></div>
                <div class="receipt__notch"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bubble__time">10:42</div>
          </div>

          <div class="bubble bubble--bot">
            <div class="bubble__text">Detect&eacute; un gasto. &iquest;Lo registro?</div>
            <div class="detected">
              <div class="detected__head"><span class="pip"></span> Movimiento OUT &middot; detectado</div>
              <div class="detected__row">
                <span>Monto</span>
                <b class="detected__amount out">S/&nbsp;87.40</b>
              </div>
              <div class="detected__row"><span>Comercio</span><b>Tottus</b></div>
              <div class="detected__row"><span>Categoria</span><b>Alimentaci&oacute;n</b></div>
              <div class="detected__row"><span>Fecha</span><b>Hoy &middot; 10:38</b></div>
              <div class="detected__actions">
                <button class="ai-btn ai-btn--green"><i data-lucide="check"></i> Confirmar</button>
                <button class="ai-btn ai-btn--ghost">Editar</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bubble__time">10:42 &middot; INOUT bot</div>
          </div>

          <div class="bubble bubble--user">
            <div class="bubble__text">gast&eacute; 45 en uber</div>
            <div class="bubble__time">10:43</div>
          </div>

          <div class="bubble bubble--bot">
            <div class="bubble__text">Listo. Registrado.</div>
            <div class="detected detected--sm">
              <div class="detected__head"><span class="pip"></span> Movimiento OUT</div>
              <div class="detected__row">
                <span>Monto</span>
                <b class="detected__amount out detected__amount--sm">S/&nbsp;45.00</b>
              </div>
              <div class="detected__row"><span>Categoria</span><b>Transporte</b></div>
            </div>
            <div class="bubble__time">10:43</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <div class="ai-features">
        <article class="ai-feat">
          <div class="ai-feat__icon green"><i data-lucide="message-square"></i></div>
          <div>
            <h3>Chatbot dentro de la app</h3>
            <p>Preguntale "&iquest;cuanto gast&eacute; en comida esta semana?" o dile "registra 80 soles de gasolina". Te responde con los numeros reales &mdash; sin abrir menus.</p>
            <span class="ai-feat__tag">Conversacion natural</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="ai-feat">
          <div class="ai-feat__icon"><i data-lucide="message-circle-more"></i></div>
          <div>
            <h3>Integraci&oacute;n con WhatsApp</h3>
            <p>Conectas tu numero una vez. Despues, registra movimientos mandando texto, audio o foto al bot. No necesitas abrir la app.</p>
            <span class="ai-feat__tag">Sin abrir la app</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="ai-feat">
          <div class="ai-feat__icon navy"><i data-lucide="scan-line"></i></div>
          <div>
            <h3>OCR por foto del recibo</h3>
            <p>La IA lee el ticket: comercio, monto, fecha. Asigna categoria por contexto. Tu solo confirmas con un toque desde el chat.</p>
            <span class="ai-feat__tag">Detecci&oacute;n autom&aacute;tica</span>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ai-section {
    background: var(--color-ink);
    color: var(--color-white-pure);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ai-section::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 64px;
    right: var(--gutter);
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
    background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15) 1.5px, transparent 1.6px);
    background-size: 16px 16px;
    opacity: 0.7;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .ai-section .wrap { position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .ai-section :global(.eyebrow-row) { color: var(--color-white-60); }
  .ai-section :global(h2) { color: var(--color-white-pure); }
  .ai-section :global(.section__lead) { color: var(--color-white-60); }

  .ai-grid {
    margin-top: 56px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr) minmax(0, 0.95fr);
    gap: clamp(32px, 5vw, 64px);
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .ai-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .chat-card {
    background: var(--color-white-pure);
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-ink-12);
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .chat-card__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-ink-12);
    background: var(--color-white-pure);
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .chat-card__avatar {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--color-ink);
    color: var(--color-white-pure);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .chat-card__avatar :global(svg) {
    width: 22px;
    height: 26px;
    color: var(--color-white-pure);
  }
  .chat-card__title {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .chat-card__sub {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-ink-60);
    margin-top: 2px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .chat-card__sub .live {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--color-primary-green);
    border-radius: 999px;
    animation: inout-blink 1.6s var(--ease-in-out) infinite;
  }
  .chat-card__verified {
    margin-left: auto;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-60);
  }
  .chat-card__verified :global(.lucide) {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    color: var(--color-primary-green);
  }

  .chat-card__body {
    padding: 22px;
    background: var(--color-sage);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .bubble {
    max-width: 88%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .bubble--user { align-self: flex-end; align-items: flex-end; }
  .bubble--bot  { align-self: flex-start; align-items: flex-start; }
  .bubble__text {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
  .bubble--user .bubble__text {
    background: var(--color-primary-green);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    border-bottom-right-radius: 6px;
  }
  .bubble--bot .bubble__text {
    background: var(--color-white-pure);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-ink-12);
    border-bottom-left-radius: 6px;
  }
  .bubble__time {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--color-ink-40);
    padding: 0 8px;
  }

  .bubble__photo {
    background: var(--color-white-pure);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-ink-12);
    border-radius: 18px;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 6px;
    padding: 8px;
    width: 200px;
  }
  .receipt {
    background: #F4F2EC;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 14px 14px 18px;
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", "SF Mono", ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    position: relative;
  }
  .receipt__title {
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .receipt__sub {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-ink-60);
    margin-top: 4px;
    font-size: 8.5px;
  }
  .receipt__sep {
    height: 1px;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--color-ink-40);
    margin: 10px 0;
  }
  .receipt__row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }
  .receipt__total {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .receipt__notch {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -8px;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 8px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 6px 0, transparent 4px, #F4F2EC 4.5px) 0 0 / 12px 8px repeat-x;
  }

  .detected {
    background: var(--color-white-pure);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-ink-12);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 14px;
    width: 260px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .detected--sm { width: 220px; }
  .detected__head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-ink-40);
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-ink-12);
  }
  .detected__head .pip {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--color-action-red);
  }
  .detected__head.in .pip { background: var(--color-primary-green); }
  .detected__row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 6px 0;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .detected__row span { color: var(--color-ink-60); }
  .detected__row b { font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); }
  .detected__amount {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 22px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .detected__amount.out { color: var(--color-action-red); }
  .detected__amount--sm { font-size: 18px; }
  .detected__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .ai-btn {
    flex: 1;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 6px;
    transition: transform 120ms var(--ease-out), background 120ms var(--ease-out);
  }
  .ai-btn--green { background: var(--color-primary-green); color: var(--color-ink); }
  .ai-btn--ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--color-ink); border: 1px solid var(--color-ink-12); }
  .ai-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }

  .ai-features { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
  .ai-feat {
    background: transparent;
    border: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-white-15);
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 28px 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 52px 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: start;
    transition: transform 120ms var(--ease-out);
  }
  .ai-feat:first-child { border-top: 0; padding-top: 0; }
  .ai-feat:hover { transform: translateX(4px); }
  .ai-feat__icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--color-white-pure);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
  }
  .ai-feat__icon.green { background: var(--color-primary-green); color: var(--color-ink); }
  .ai-feat__icon.navy  { background: var(--color-navy-deep); color: var(--color-white-pure); }
  .ai-feat__icon :global(.lucide) { width: 24px; height: 24px; stroke-width: 2; }
  .ai-feat h3 {
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
    margin: 4px 0 8px;
    color: var(--color-white-pure);
  }
  .ai-feat p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--color-white-60);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .ai-feat__tag {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--color-primary-green);
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
</style>
